import { IconLogo, Menu, MenuItem, MenuItemLink, NavbarContainer, NavbarWrapper } from "./Navbar.elements"
import { AiFillAliwangwang } from "react-icons/ai";

const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <NavbarContainer>
                <NavbarWrapper>
                    <IconLogo>
                        <AiFillAliwangwang size={"2em"}/>
                        Javi-p(x)
                    </IconLogo>
                        <Menu>
                            <MenuItem>
                                <MenuItemLink>
                                    Home
                                </MenuItemLink>
                            </MenuItem>
                        </Menu>
                </NavbarWrapper>
            </NavbarContainer>
        </>
    )
}

export default Navbar
